      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study yielded GCI of 3.1% on volume-averaged shear stress for the medium mesh. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence regime. Discretization error is within the 5% acceptance threshold for MRL 2. Medium mesh (5.8M elements) adopted for all production simulations."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
