      "rationale": "FDA GCBP test conditions documented in Morrison et al. (2019). Five flow-speed combinations (2–6 L/min at 2000–3500 RPM) tested using bovine blood with hematocrit 33±2%. Flow measured with Coriolis meter (±0.5% FS), speed with optical tachometer (±5 RPM). Fluid temperature maintained at 37±0.5°C. All instruments NIST-traceable."
