      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index compared between CFD predictions and experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 6.3%, maximum error 9.1% at the highest flow-speed combination. All predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Validation metric M computed per ASME V&V 20 methodology confirms adequate agreement at MRL 2."
