      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals monitored; solver error deemed negligible relative to discretization error at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals for continuity, momentum, and turbulence equations converged to 1e-5 or better in all production runs. Solver error is considered negligible relative to the 3.1% discretization uncertainty and is scoped out per MRL 2 guidelines."
    },
    {
