    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 guidelines. Validation evidence demonstrates RH prediction error of 6.3% mean absolute error across all 5 operating points, within the 10% acceptance band. The CFD model is accepted as fit for purpose for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Uncertainty quantification has been declared at the package level; sensitivity analysis with respect to hemolysis model constants is planned for the MRL 3 submission but is not required at MRL 2.",
